author: Arman Azad, CNN
title: Coronavirus death rate is lower than previously reported, study says, but it's still deadlier than seasonal flu
description: How many people die after being infected with the novel coronavirus? Fewer than previously calculated, according to a study released Monday, but still more than die from the flu.
content:
